<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-1405] Support for new Resources model in ant 1.7 in Lucene ant task.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-1405</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;Ant Task for Lucene should use modern Resource model (not only FileSet child element).&lt;br/&gt;
There is a patch with required changes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Supported by old (ant 1.6) and new (ant 1.7) resources model:&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;index ....&amp;gt; &amp;lt;!-- Lucene Ant Task --&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;fileset ... /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/index&amp;gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Supported only by new (ant 1.7) resources model:&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;index ....&amp;gt; &amp;lt;!-- Lucene Ant Task --&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;filelist ... /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/index&amp;gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;index ....&amp;gt; &amp;lt;!-- Lucene Ant Task --&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;userdefinied-filesource ... /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/index&amp;gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description>
